childMarkdownRemark.html: This is a repackaged ONLYOFFICE Workspace with professional support for your business. ONLYOFFICE Workspace is a free open-source collaborative system developed to manage documents, projects, customer relationship and email correspondence, all in one place. It allows you to organize business tasks and milestones, store and share your corporate or personal documents, use social networking tools such as blogs and forums, as well as communicate with your team members via corporate IM.
